NAME
  abundle - link a multi-module Lua project into one file

SYNOPSIS
  abundle <entry.lua> <out.lua> [--minify]

DESCRIPTION
  Statically resolves require() calls, embeds every local module into
  package.preload and appends the entry chunk. Modules it cannot find locally
  (e.g. component, filesystem) stay as runtime requires. --minify shrinks the
  result with aminify.
